   ✅ AI Engine
   ✅ Code Executor
   ✅ Self Trainer
   ✅ Web Scraper
   🎉 All systems ready!
   
   ==================================================
   🚀 AI Code Generator API V2.0
   ==================================================
   📖 Docs: http://localhost:8000/docs
   🔌 WebSocket: ws://localhost:8000/ws/{session_id}
   ==================================================
   
   INFO: Uvicorn running on http://0.0.0.0:8000

5. เห็นอย่างนี้ = API พร้อมแล้ว!

⚠️ ห้ามปิด Terminal นี้! ต้องเปิดค้างไว้
```

