## STEP 25: ใช้งาน API ผ่าน Python

### 25.1 เรียกใช้ API
```
>>> import requests

# Generate Code
>>> response = requests.post(
...     "http://localhost:8000/generate",
...     json={
...         "instruction": "สร้าง web scraper",
...         "language": "python"
...     }
... )
>>> result = response.json()
>>> print(result['data']['code'])

# Chat
>>> response = requests.post(
...     "http://localhost:8000/chat",
...     json={
...         "message": "สอนเขียน API ด้วย FastAPI",
...         "session_id": "user1"
...     }
... )
>>> print(response.json()['response'])

# Execute Code
>>> response = requests.post(
...     "http://localhost:8000/execute",
...     json={
...         "code": "print('Hello')",
...         "language": "python"
...     }
... )
>>> print(response.json()['result']['stdout'])

# Analyze File
>>> files = {'file': open('test.py', 'rb')}
>>> response = requests.post(
...     "http://localhost:8000/analyze/file",
...     files=files
... )
>>> print(response.json()['analysis'])
```

